on-arrival: time_to_election = 3; spd_in_government = 0; in_grand_coalition = 0; in_weimar_coalition = 0; in_popular_front = 0; spd_toleration = 0; spd_toleration_right = 0; coalition_dissent = 0; pro_republic -= 5; old_middle_spd -= 3; new_middle_spd -= 2; workers_spd -= 3 if pro_republic < 50; workers_spd -= 4 if pro_republic < 40; old_middle_nsdap += 4 if pro_republic < 50; new_middle_nsdap += 3 if pro_republic < 50; lvp_right += 3; ddp_right += 2; ddp_cohesion -= 1; dvp_right += 3

Мы отправили Брюнинга в отставку и назначили новые выборы на [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +].


@bruning_chain
view-if: not constructive_vonc and not (right_coalition >= 50 and (dnvp_ideology == "Умеренные" or dnvp_westarp) and not (year = 1929 and month >= 7)) and not ((center_right_coalition >= 50 and right_coalition < 50) and dnvp_ideology == "Умеренные" and not (year = 1929 and month >= 7)) and (not bruning_event_seen and year >= 1930)
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0; minority_government = 1; grand_coalition_collapsed = 1 if in_grand_coalition; in_grand_coalition = 0; in_weimar_coalition = 0; coalition_dissent = 0; chancellor = "Брюнинг"; chancellor_party = "Центр"; foreign_minister_party = "ННП"; foreign_minister_party = "ЛНП" if lvp_formed; interior_minister_party = "Центр"; justice_minister_party = "I"; labor_minister_party = "Центр"; reichswehr_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = ddp_name; economic_minister_party = "ЛНП" if lvp_formed; finance_minister_party = "ННП"; finance_minister_party = "ЛНП" if lvp_formed; agriculture_minister_party = "Центр"; bruning_event_timer = 6 if not bruning_event_seen and year >= 1930

На смену нам пришел Брюнинг из[? if z_party_name != "ХНП": <span style="color: #000000;">Партии Центра</span> ?][? if z_party_name == "ХНП": <span style="color: #000000;">**ХНП**</span> ?], который реорганизовал кабинет, включив в него буржуазные партии. [? if not bruning_event_seen and year >= 1930: Новые выборы ещё не назначены, но, вероятно, их скоро объявят, учитывая, что Брюнинг, скорее всего, не имеет поддержки большинства в рейхстаге. ?]


@tolerate
view-if: not constructive_vonc and (bruning_event_seen or year < 1930)
choose-if: not (right_coalition >= 50 and bourgeois_coalition < 50 and (dnvp_ideology == "Умеренные" or dnvp_westarp) and not (year = 1929 and month >= 7)) and not (right_coalition < 50 and center_right_coalition >= 50 and bourgeois_coalition < 50 and dnvp_ideology == "Умеренные" and not (year = 1929 and month >= 7))
unavailable-subtitle: Мы им не нужны.
